Since 1999, we have been using WIMS in large-scale teaching experiences on 300-400 first-year students of Sciences major in <a href="https://univ-cotedazur.fr">Université de Nice - Sophia Antipolis</a>,
for one-semester courses consisting of 1 or 2 weekly sessions of 90 minutes in computer rooms (individual workstation for each student).

